{"tid":1553425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民賤聯提倡設立「監師會」製造白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:30:09.000Z","uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8fe1df9227041f303065acd8f30ff418bdbbc6f","tid":1553425,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>教協譴責民建聯倡設「監師會」　斥推卸政治責任予教師</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員<span style=\"color: blue;\">李慧琼</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">葛珮帆</span>及部分警隊家屬昨日與3名局長會面，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求教育局成立「監師會」及在課室設置錄影及錄音設備等</span>。教協對此表示強烈譴責，要求民建聯停止<span style=\"color: gold;\">推卸政治責任到教育界</span>。<br />\n<br />\n教協表示，現時教師受到校方、教育人員專業操守議會及教育局監察，有既定程序處理專業操守問題，沒有需要另設「監師會」。教協批評，<span style=\"color: gold;\">在課堂裝設錄音及錄影設備，令教師和學生被監控的情況下授課和學習，會在學校製造白色恐怖</span>。<br />\n<br />\n教協強烈反對因為任何政治原因修改課程內容，認為現時課程內容和規劃已有行之有效的檢討方式，並按照教育專業自主的原則定期檢視。教協強調本港教師均十分專業，以持平的態度進行教育工作，若有教師被投訴，亦有機制跟進。<br />\n<br />\n教協表示，對民建聯的建議感到震驚及憤怒，<span style=\"color: gold;\">認為他們罔顧教育界的實際情況，以政治凌駕專業，形容他們隨意為教師扣上「煽動學生上街」的帽子，試圖把反修例風暴的責任強加教育界</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>反問民建聯會否要求所有警務人員收回對市民的仇恨言論，並向公眾致歉</em></span>。<br />\n<br />\nSource from RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479503-20190908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479503-20190908.htm&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BklZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=056ffa4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479503-20190908.htm&h=f83d19c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479503-20190908.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n到底建制派呢班親共賣港嘅傀儡政客出賣香港可以出賣到咩嘅地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a69ed6c39cb8b21d69c63697e6b5aa2689959e","tid":1553425,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"黎啦，快d成立啦，嫌個火唔夠旺啦"},{"pid":"bd5454d573f8ddc97e5b98f57e55b1eecc4b6f6d","tid":1553425,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>叫阿爺阿嫲阿公阿婆阿爸阿媽投</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edu5dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edu5dD.png&h=f7e4a997&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}